title: The service may change its terms at any time, but the user will receive notification of the changes.
quoteText:
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time.
If we make any material changes, we will use commercially reasonable efforts to notify you, by means of a notice on the Service.
Those changes will go into effect on the “Last updated” date shown at the top of the updated Privacy Policy.
Your continued use of the Service constitutes your consent to be bound by the revised Privacy Policy.
